item.description:
@d_man103456 wrote:

If I remember right, I haven’t added portals in a while, find the ID of the portal and make a case for it

case 1812: teleportToX = 1234; teleportToY = 4321; break;
now of course you can make it more fancy with animations and gfxs but that is the just of what you need. You may have to change the teleportToX to teleToX or w\e it is on your source.
